{"_path":"/maps/_database/deltalake/deltalake","_dir":"deltalake","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Delta Lake","description":"一个开源的存储层，旨在为数据湖提供 ACID 事务支持、可扩展的元数据处理和统一的批处理与流处理能力。","original_path":"content/6.maps/_database/delta-lake/delta-lake.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"主题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主题"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"./liquid-clustering"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Delta Lake Liquid Clustering"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - 动态数据布局优化技术"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"概述"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"概述"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Delta Lake 是一个开源的存储层，旨在为数据湖提供 ACID 事务支持、可扩展的元数据处理和统一的批处理与流处理能力。它构建在现有数据湖存储（如 S3、HDFS、Azure Data Lake Storage）之上，通过添加事务日志和版本控制，解决了传统数据湖在数据一致性、数据质量和性能方面的挑战。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"主题","depth":2,"text":"主题"},{"id":"概述","depth":2,"text":"概述"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_database:deltalake:deltalake.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_database/deltalake/deltalake.md","_stem":"6.maps/_database/deltalake/deltalake","_extension":"md"}